      - 21
    kind: assumption
    message: IrTest/Ir only derive PartialEq, not Eq, since they hold serde_json::Value.
    reasoning: Prompt says all types 'support equality comparison' without specifying PartialEq vs Eq. IrType/IrFunction (pure Strings) derive PartialEq+Eq, but IrTest/Ir contain serde_json::Value, which has no Eq impl, so only PartialEq could be derived for them. Agent assumed this relaxation was acceptable rather than flagging a conflict.
    suggestion: Note that types containing serde_json::Value need only derive PartialEq (Value has no Eq), while pure-string types should derive both PartialEq and Eq.
  - promptLines:
