    kind: assumption
    message: Added Debug and Clone derives beyond what prompt required.
    reasoning: Prompt only asked for Deserialize and equality comparison. Agent additionally derived Debug and Clone on all types for ergonomics (e.g. test assertions, error messages), which is a reasonable but unrequested addition.
  - promptLines:
