    kind: assumption
    message: Error type shape (enum with Deserialize/EmptyModule/InvalidTestValue variants) was invented, not specified.
    reasoning: Prompt only requires validate_ir return 'an error on failure (an error value, never a panic)' without specifying its structure. Agent designed a custom IrValidationError enum with Display/Error impls and a field name in InvalidTestValue; a different but equally valid error shape (e.g. a single String error) could have been chosen instead.
